      </ul>

      <p>NVIDIA is the foundational play but may consolidate after recent gains. Iron condor collects premium while theta works in your favor.</p>

      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-3">Oracle Synthetic Long (Software Enabler)</h3>

      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-gray-300 ml-4">
        <li><strong class="text-white">Structure:</strong> Sell cash-secured puts at $135 strike</li>
